* An {@link ExercisePerformanceGoal} that requires a target RPE (rate of perceived exertion) to * be met during the associated {@link PlannedExerciseStep}. * *

Values correspond to the Borg CR10 RPE scale and must be in the range 0 to 10 inclusive. * 0: No exertion (at rest) 1: Very light 2-3: Light 4-5: Moderate 6-7: Hard 8-9: Very hard 10: * Maximum effort

methods.name: public int getRpe()
methods.comment: * @return Target RPE that should be met.
